STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Donald Edward MCINTYRE, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0266 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

The defendant appeals his conviction for robbery in the first degree. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
